name: Crop consulting
description: Soil sample analysis and good maps are the foundation for building a strong crop plan, so these are the first components of the plan that we focus on.

name: Soil sampling
description: Good decisions start with good data. Good fertility and nutrient management data start with taking good samples. Book now before it get's too late!

name: Enviromental planning
description: A plan that insures nutrients are used agronomically on the crops with minimal erosion, and insures nutrients are not lost from the farmstead.

name: Precision agriculture
description: Precision agriculture is site specific crop management focused on managing field variability. Precision agriculture uses modern technology.
